cs.FL, cs.DS, cs.LO, cs.IT, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automata and series recognition. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a likely category as the paper discusses effective procedures for building automata. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with decidability of equality. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with series over a field of real numbers. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with max-plus and min-plus systems.
